   value=""/><BODY><TEXT>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img style="height: auto;" src="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-46885305_1" alt="" width="526" height="351"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span bb:beforeshowfunc="" bb:overwritenavitems="" bb:menuorder="openId_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,open_with_browser_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,open_with_bbdrive_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,openWebId_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,view360Id_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,*separator*,*separator*,ax-ally-placeholder_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,ax-ally-markForAxAnalysis_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,*separator*,*separator*,content_settings_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,content_editSettings_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,content_edit_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,properties_folder_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,itemcarot_managerecord_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,comments_tool_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,subscriptions_list_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,content_readfile_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,content_overwrite_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,passes_tool_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,permissions_tool_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,content_add_alignment_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,content_tracking_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,content_versions_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,*separator*,*separator*,bookmarkId_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,itemsId_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,packagesId_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,emailId_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,removeContentFolderId_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,*separator*,copyContentId_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,moveContentId_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,*separator*,removeContentId_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,*separator*,Metadata_General_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,Metadata_Dublin_Core_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,Metadata_IMS_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726,Metadata_Full_IMS_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726," bb:contextparameters="" bb:navitem="" bb:menugeneratorurl="/webapps/cmsmain/webui/courses/15_U_JTE_VU23217_1/CSIRO_ScienceImage_2041_A_man_looking_at_a_tablet_in_an_energy_facility.jpg?action=details&amp;amp;subaction=generateFileMenuItem&amp;amp;uniq=ts9hlj&amp;amp;course_id=_35184_1&amp;amp;ctxMenuXythosId=42081385_1&amp;amp;course_id=_35184_1"&gt;&lt;a title="Click for more options" href="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@webapps/blackboard/content/listContentEditable.jsp?course_id=_35184_1&amp;amp;content_id=_3540621_1#contextMenu" role="button" id="cmlink_9ebe827a9ca642ec8f9b6103edaf4726"&gt;&lt;img style="height: 14px; width: 16px;" alt="Click for more options" src="https://learn.content.blackboardcdn.com/3900.56.0-rel.31+e33c6d6/images/ci/icons/cmlink_generic.gif"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span bb:menugeneratorurl="/webapps/cmsmain/webui/courses/15_U_JTE_VU23217_1/CSIRO_ScienceImage_2041_A_man_looking_at_a_tablet_in_an_energy_facility.jpg?action=details&amp;amp;subaction=generateFileMenuItem&amp;amp;uniq=-p686a3&amp;amp;course_id=_35184_1&amp;amp;ctxMenuXythosId=42081385_1&amp;amp;course_id=_35184_1" bb:navitem="" bb:contextparameters="" bb:menuorder="openId_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,open_with_browser_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,open_with_bbdrive_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,openWebId_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,view360Id_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,*separator*,*separator*,ax-ally-placeholder_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,ax-ally-markForAxAnalysis_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,*separator*,*separator*,content_settings_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,content_editSettings_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,content_edit_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,properties_folder_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,itemcarot_managerecord_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,comments_tool_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,subscriptions_list_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,content_readfile_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,content_overwrite_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,passes_tool_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,permissions_tool_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,content_add_alignment_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,content_tracking_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,content_versions_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,*separator*,*separator*,bookmarkId_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,itemsId_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,packagesId_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,emailId_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,removeContentFolderId_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,*separator*,copyContentId_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,moveContentId_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,*separator*,removeContentId_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,*separator*,Metadata_General_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,Metadata_Dublin_Core_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,Metadata_IMS_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7,Metadata_Full_IMS_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7," bb:overwritenavitems="" bb:beforeshowfunc=""&gt;&lt;a id="cmlink_7d986c83a21745b594fe3500ff2227d7" role="button" href="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@webapps/blackboard/content/listContentEditable.jsp?content_id=_3540621_1&amp;amp;course_id=_35184_1#contextMenu" title="Click for more options"&gt;&lt;img style="height: 14px; width: 16px;" src="https://learn.content.blackboardcdn.com/3900.56.0-rel.31+e33c6d6/images/ci/icons/cmlink_generic.gif" alt="Click for more options"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;br&gt;What this course is all about&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;div&gt;This unit deals with the performance outcome, knowledge and skills required to recognise threats, risks and vulnerabilities to cyber security in an organisation.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;The threats to an organisation include networks, machines, applications, data, users and infrastructure.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Common cyber security attack mechanisms and an introduction to threat management as well as security issues surrounding Internet of Things (IoT) devices are addressed.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;The implementation of tools and systems an organisation can use for protection against cyber-attacks are also investigated.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;(Images - CSIRO)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h6&gt;Day 1 - Step by Step&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;div&gt;Your lecturer will introduce expectations of subject.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: 400; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;Together you will go through the Unit Learning &amp;amp; Assessment Plan (found under "Welcome") and analyse assessment requirements.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;It is important that you listen to the lecturer's expectations for each assessment submission.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;You have five TASKS or labs which are &lt;strong&gt;Required&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;as part of the Assessment 1 Portfolio of Tasks.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;An important first principle of security - &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;There is no such thing as absolute security&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Consider the implications of&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IBM predictions of quantum computers&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;(see link in Slide 4 of the PowerPoint below)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In Session Activity:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol style="list-style-type: decimal;"&gt;&lt;li style="list-style-type: inherit;"&gt;Recorgnise the need for cyber security. &lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://ia.acs.org.au/article/2023/poor-security-led-to-pathology-hack.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Poor security led to pathology hack and prosecution | Information Age | ACS&lt;/a&gt; -&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a alt="" href="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-72018979_1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Poor security led to pathology hack and prosecution.docx&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="list-style-type: inherit;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;Similar story, different regulator prosecuting for poor cyber security&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;, &lt;a href="https://ia.acs.org.au/article/2025/asic-sues-company-over-prolonged-cybersecurity-failures.html?ref=newsletter&amp;amp;deliveryName=DM25581" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;ASIC sues company over prolonged cybersecurity failures | Information Age | ACS&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="list-style-type: inherit;"&gt;Even large Aussi government agencies need to improve their cyber security &lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://ia.acs.org.au/article/2024/govt-agencies-unprepared-for--significant--cyber-incident.html?ref=newsletter&amp;amp;deliveryName=DM22265" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Govt agencies unprepared for ‘significant’ cyber incident | Information Age | ACS&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="list-style-type: inherit;"&gt;What does Cyber security involve? View&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Cyber&amp;nbsp;Security&amp;nbsp;Body&amp;nbsp;of&amp;nbsp;Knowledge (CyBoK)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span bb:menugeneratorurl="/webapps/cmsmain/webui/courses/15_C_JTE_VU21990_1/cybok.docx?action=details&amp;amp;subaction=generateFileMenuItem&amp;amp;uniq=b0v6tf&amp;amp;course_id=_17452_1&amp;amp;ctxMenuXythosId=18903234_1&amp;amp;course_id=_17452_1" bb:navitem="" bb:contextparameters="" bb:menuorder="openId_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,open_with_browser_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,open_with_bbdrive_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,openWebId_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,view360Id_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,*separator*,*separator*,ax-ally-placeholder_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,ax-ally-markForAxAnalysis_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,*separator*,*separator*,content_settings_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,content_editSettings_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,content_edit_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,properties_folder_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,itemcarot_managerecord_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,comments_tool_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,subscriptions_list_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,content_readfile_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,content_overwrite_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,passes_tool_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,permissions_tool_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,content_add_alignment_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,content_tracking_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,content_versions_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,*separator*,*separator*,bookmarkId_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,itemsId_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,packagesId_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,emailId_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,removeContentFolderId_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,*separator*,copyContentId_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,moveContentId_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,*separator*,removeContentId_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,*separator*,Metadata_General_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,Metadata_Dublin_Core_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,Metadata_IMS_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83,Metadata_Full_IMS_e5c3e4722f6b4ff0aa12d6cce68ece83," bb:overwritenavitems="" bb:beforeshowfunc=""&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-51825987_1" width="772" height="814"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="list-style-type: inherit;"&gt;Enrol in&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Cisco&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Cybersecurity Essentials&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;. Have a look at the&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Course Index&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;noting what is in each of the 8 chapters.&lt;br&gt;Also note this&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Recognise the Need for Cyber Security&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;unit does NOT include all the&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Cybersecurity Essentials&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;chapters nor are you expected or required to complete the&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Cybersecurity Essentials&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;assessments.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a rel="noopener" target="_blank" href="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-25008812_1" alt=""&gt;Enrolling using the Seat Token.docx&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;See&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Out of Session Activities&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;below for first session reading and actions.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;h6&gt;Important Learnings&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;ol style="list-style-type: decimal;"&gt;&lt;li style="list-style-type: inherit;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Security Principles: CIA Triad&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;- examine the definitions of&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Confidentiality, Integrity and Availability&lt;/strong&gt; and how they apply as concepts to Information Security.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="list-style-type: inherit;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 13.3333px;"&gt;CISCO&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Cybersecrity Essentials&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 13.3333px;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;Readings and actions:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;ul style="list-style-type: disc;"&gt;&lt;li style="list-style-type: none;"&gt;&lt;ul style="list-style-type: disc;"&gt;&lt;li style="list-style-type: circle;"&gt;Attempt Chapter 1 Quiz&amp;nbsp;before&amp;nbsp;reading any of the Chapter. Note what you did and didn't know to answer&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="list-style-type: circle;"&gt;Active Reading: 1.2.1 Cybersecurity Criminals (3 pages)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="list-style-type: circle;"&gt;Active Reading: 1.3.1 Threat Arenas (6 pages)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="list-style-type: circle;"&gt;Attempt&amp;nbsp;Chapter 2 Quiz&amp;nbsp;before&amp;nbsp;reading any of the Chapter. Note what you did and didn't know to answer&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="list-style-type: circle;"&gt;Active Reading: 2.0 Introduction (1 page)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="list-style-type: circle;"&gt;Active Reading: 2.1 (3 pages)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h6&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Out of Session Activities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;ul style="list-style-type: disc;"&gt;&lt;li style="list-style-type: inherit;"&gt;Complete the&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Cybersecurity Essentials&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;Chapter 1 and 2 readings listed above.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="list-style-type: inherit;"&gt;Complete the Cisco activity&amp;nbsp; "1.5.1.3 Activity - Identify the NIST/NICE Cybersecurity Specialty Areas"&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;Further Discussion questions&amp;nbsp;(If no time in session, read at home. Discuss next week):&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;ul style="list-style-type: disc;"&gt;&lt;li style="list-style-type: inherit;"&gt;How have privacy laws changes since the Universal Declaration of Human Rights : Article 12 Right to Privacy&amp;nbsp; (1948)?&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="list-style-type: inherit;"&gt;What effect are IOT and AI having on data protection risk?&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div&gt;If interested in how bots work view this video by CGP Grey &lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R9OHn5ZF4Uo" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;How bots work - CGP Grey&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;If interested in quantum computing, start with this, &lt;a href="https://www.google.com/search?q=quantum+computing+update+2024&amp;amp;rlz=1CAKCXJ_enAU1145AU1145&amp;amp;oq=quantum+computer+update&amp;amp;gs_lcrp=EgZjaHJvbWUqCAgBEAAYFhgeMgkIABBFGDkYgAQyCAgBEAAYFhgeMggIAhAAGBYYHjIICAMQABgWGB4yDQgEEAAYhgMYgAQYigUyDQgFEAAYhgMYgAQYigUyBwgGEAAY7wUyCggHEAAYgAQYogQyCggIEAAYgAQYogQyCggJEAAYgAQYogTSAQkxMzg5OWowajSoAgCwAgE&amp;amp;sourceid=chrome&amp;amp;ie=UTF-8#fpstate=ive&amp;amp;vld=cid:5514be2c,vid:tIJuyb5DWUw,st:0" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;2024 Quantum Computing Update - Explaining Computers - YouTube&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp; (15 minutes)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;This article from mid July gives further reasons why quantum computing is a worry for cyber security people.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;a rel="noopener" target="_blank" href="https://ia.acs.org.au/content/ia/article/2021/quantum-decryption-coming.html?ref=newsletter"&gt;https://ia.acs.org.au/content/ia/article/2021/quantum-decryption-coming.html?ref=newsletter&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</TEXT><TYPE
